snippet.title: Second Stellar - Reveal Teaser
snippet.description:
Wishlist Second Stellar on Steam now! https://store.steampowered.com/app/3176850/Second_Stellar/
Join the Second Stellar Discord Server as well! https://discord.gg/invite/rBjDqQ9TfP

Join twin Starfarers Asphodene and Eridani as they traverse the cosmos in this unique action roguelite, unraveling the mysteries of their galaxy and beyond in pursuit of the Voyager.
